      ],
      "source": "https://debary.org/309/DeBary-History"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "DeBary Hall, a 20‑room estate built in 1871, now serves as a museum and event venue and was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1972.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2,
        13,
        8
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2",
