      ],
      "source": "https://grokipedia.com/page/DeBary,_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The town sits on the eastern shore of the St. Johns River, near Lake Monroe, where the Timucua people once lived before being displaced in the 1700s.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        14,
        17,
        18,
        19
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia",
