        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DeBary%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "In 1876, de Bary launched the DeBary Merchants' Line, a steamboat service that carried mail between Jacksonville and Enterprise along the St. Johns River.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        29,
        30
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
