        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DeBary%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "DeBary is part of the Deltona–Daytona Beach–Ormond Beach metropolitan area, which had a population of 553,284 in 2019.",
